SEARCH
Package antlr

Class IRTXTBaseListener

java.lang.Object
antlr.IRTXTBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRTXTListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class IRTXTBaseListener extends Object implements IRTXTListener
This class provides an empty implementation of IRTXTListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
